<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hey <%=@account.first_name%>!</h1>
    <%if @time_frame == "week"%>
      <p>
        Good news, you are on the schedule in a week! Take a look below to
        confirm the times that we have for you to work. Please give us a call
        if you have any questions or need to talk about you schedule.
      </p>
    <%else%>
      <p>
        Just a quick reminder about your work that is happening tomorrow. As
        always, please give us a call if there is any issues.
      </p>
    <%end%>
    <ul>
      <%@activities.each do |activity|%>
        <li>
          <%=activity.day_and_time_span%> - <%=activity.name%>
        </li>
      <%end%>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>
